arStrings.szText: “I bring dark tidings from the Fractured Peaks…”
Rathma is dead? I brought the Prophecy to Inarius so he could unravel its true meaning. I never expected he would kill his son because of it.
Shocked at the knowledge Rathma, something of a demigod, is dead.
And now the very thing he wanted, this infernal key to Hell, is in Lilith’s hands. It must relate to her search for Astaroth…
